    content:
        'As college students, our lives revolve around lectures, assignments, and, of course, food! Whether grabbing a quick bite between classes or enjoying a leisurely meal after a long day, the food spots in and around our campus are essential for keeping us fuelled and happy. On-Campus Delights The Farmer’s Fresh Cafeteria: Shahi paneer, Kadhai paneer, Paneer bhurji, Kadhai chicken, Snack options like noodles, spring rolls The Burger House: Burgers, Wraps, Pizzas, Chilled mojitos The Kerala Canteen: Idlis and vadas, Masala dosa Juice Corner and Desi Urban Chai: Shakes and juices, Chai and coffee with various flavors Maggi Point, Coffee Day, Dubey Canteen: Various flavors of Maggi, Coffees, brownies, and pastries, Food available until 3 am at Dubey Canteen Outside Campus Delights The Backyard: A great place for celebrations Bella Chowk: Main market with food brands like Subway and Domino\'s Shagun Dhaba: Serves delicious Chicken Biryani with raita Heritage Haveli: Presents top-quality food on Chandigarh-Ropar highway Zomato and Swiggy: Alternatives for food delivery So, stop reading and start the journey of devouring it all. Bon Appétit!',
