        'Revanche, is a two day adventure where you can expect to have the time of life! With hundreds of teams and skilled players battling it out, on the fields of BGMI and COD, in the intense duels of Clash Royale and an offline FIFA competition hosted on state-of-the-art PC setups, you just might escape reality! Have you ever tested you balance and agility on a Hoverboard? Gathered around the warmth of a bonfire with live music being played to set the mood just right and just relaxed and socialised for a while? You can do that and more and end this 2 day journey of yours with an electrifying DJ night ensuring everyone leaves on a high note! PHOTO GALLERY',
