    content:
        'General Store Welcome to the General Store: your one-stop-shop for everything you didn\'t know you needed, from midnight snacks to last-minute party essentials! Open from 10 am to 8 pm, we\'ve got you covered from some essential garments to gadgets, and everything in between. Need a midnight snack or a morning pick-me-up? We\'ll be here, ready to fulfil your every need with a smile! Stationery Shop Welcome to the Stationary Sanctuary! Need a calculator for quantum physics or a ruler for precise circuit diagrams? We\'ve got you covered from pencils to protractors, open from dawn till dusk (8 am - 8 pm) to fuel your academic adventures. Just remember, we can\'t provide solution',
